<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-1947] Snowball package contains BSD licensed code with ASL header</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-1947</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;All classes in org.tartarus.snowball (but not in org.tartarus.snowball.ext) has for some reason been given an ASL header. These classes are licensed with BSD. Thus the ASL header should be removed. I suppose this a misstake or possible due to the ASL header automation tool.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
